reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fast and reliable - perfect for the iPhone 15
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the SAMSUNG Type-C USB Flash Drive, and I am impressed with its performance and features.**Speed Demon:**This little blue wonder lives up to its promise of lightning-fast data transfers. The up to 400MB/s read speeds make it an absolute game-changer for anyone who values their time. Note that the write speeds are significantly slower.**Universal Compatibility:**I appreciate the USB type-c compatibility, making it future-proof and ensuring seamless connections with modern devices. The backward compatibility with USB 3.0/2.0 ensures it works with a wide range of devices.**Waterproof Marvel:**Accidents happen, but with this drive, I know my data is safe, come rain or shine. It's a relief to have a tech device that can weather the storm.**Generous Storage:**With 256GB of storage, this flash drive is a portable powerhouse. Whether it's documents, photos, or backups, there's ample space to accommodate my needs without constantly worrying about running out of room.**Sturdy Build:**The build quality is top-notch. It feels sturdy in hand, and the robust construction gives me confidence that it can withstand the rigors of daily use.**Sleek Design:**The sleek blue design is not just about aesthetics; it also makes the drive easy to spot in a cluttered bag. The retractable design protects the USB connector when not in use, adding an extra layer of durability. One thing to note is it does not fit through my Lamicall protective case. I purchased an extender to make it fit.In conclusion, the SAMSUNG Type-C USB Flash Drive is a stellar combination of speed, reliability, and durability. If you're in need of a high-performance flash drive that doesn't compromise on design and comes with the added bonus of being waterproof, look no further. This is a must-have gadget for anyone who values efficiency and peace of mind in their digital life!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I only trust Samsung with my pictures and sensitive info
reviews.reviewText: This is the Samsung brand we all have grown to love with their jaw-dropping TVs and must-have cutting-edge Galaxy line phones. Samsung has been the number 1 brand in flash drives since 2003. You can count on your priceless pictures transferring with zero errors or corrupt files.Honestly, the price of these Samsung flash drives is cheap. The quality, reliability, and performance are what make Samsung. I bought two of these.They are so easy to use. They have a unmount option you select when you want to unplug the flash drive and just plug it back in when you want to use it. They work on phones, tablets, cameras, desktops, laptops, and Im sure other devices.It's magnet, x-ray, water, heat & and cold, and impact-proof. It's pretty much indestructible unless you're going to blow it up or shoot it with a gun. I seriously doubt you'll be doing any of that but if you do, invite me I'm free.I'm sure another brand has one faster or holds more pictures. But do they have two decades of being the world's number 1 brand? Nope, they sure don't. So do yourself a favor and buy a couple of these and back up your pictures. You know the ones that can't be replaced. This flash drive will accept 4K video as well.Oh, and I almost forgot. The look of it is pretty cool too. It fits between your fingers nicely and it's very very easy to use. And its small enough to fit on your key chain or even a neckless.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Blazing Fast and Spacious Samsung Type-C USB Flash Drive
reviews.reviewText: I recently acquired the Samsung Type-C USB Flash Drive, boasting a capacious 256GB storage capacity and the ability to transfer 4GB files in a jaw-dropping 11 seconds, thanks to its astonishing speed of up to 400MB/s. It's safe to say that this little device has left me profoundly impressed.First and foremost, the transfer speed is nothing short of remarkable. Whether it's moving hefty media files or backing up important documents, this flash drive delivers unrivaled performance. It's a game-changer for anyone who values their time and appreciates the convenience of swift data transfers.The inclusion of a Type-C connector is a brilliant choice. With the increasing prevalence of Type-C ports on modern devices, this flash drive ensures seamless compatibility across a wide range of laptops, smartphones, and tablets. No more fumbling around for the right USB port – it's as plug-and-play as it gets.The sleek and durable design of this Samsung flash drive is another plus. The brushed metal finish not only looks stylish but also feels robust in hand. Plus, it's small and compact, making it incredibly portable. I can easily slip it into my pocket or attach it to my keychain, ensuring my essential files are always within arm's reach.The 256GB storage capacity is more than generous. It's ample space for my photos, videos, documents, and then some. Whether I'm storing my entire multimedia library or a hefty work project, this flash drive has space to spare.In terms of reliability, Samsung's reputation for quality precedes it. I have confidence that my data is safe and secure on this flash drive, and the build quality inspires trust.This Samsung Type-C USB Flash Drive is a revelation in the world of portable storage. Its speed, compatibility, and spaciousness make it a standout choice for anyone seeking a dependable solution for data transfer and storage needs. With this flash drive in your pocket, you're not just getting a storage device – you're getting a reliable, high-performance companion for all your digital adventures. Highly recommended!
